#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-pimdataexporter; allows to export and import PIM settings and local "
"mail. You can backup and restore settings from the following programs:"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-pimdataexporter; omogoča izvoz in uvoz nastavitev PIM in lokalne "
"pošte. Nastavitve lahko varnostno kopirate in obnovite iz naslednjih "
"programov:"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail;"
msgstr "&kmail;"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "&knotes;"
msgstr "&knotes;"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "&akregator;"
msgstr "&akregator;"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kaddressbook;"
msgstr "&kaddressbook;"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalarm;"
msgstr "&kalarm;"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "&korganizer;"
msgstr "&korganizer;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &i18n-pimdataexporter;"
msgstr "Uporaba &i18n-pimdataexporter;ja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Backing up is an essential practice for all users. &i18n-pimdataexporter; is "
"a great tool for backing up or moving all of your settings and email to a "
"new installation. You also use &i18n-pimdataexporter; to import previous "
"backups."
msgstr ""
"Varnostno kopiranje je bistvena praksa za vse uporabnike. &i18n-"
"pimdataexporter; je odlično orodje za varnostno kopiranje ali premikanje "
"vseh vaših nastavitev in e-pošte v novo namestitev. &i18n-pimdataexporter; "
"se uporablja tudi za uvoz prejšnjih varnostnih kopij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export &kmail; "
"Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> through the message view window or &i18n-"
"pimdataexporter; can be run as a standalone application by running &i18n-"
"pimdataexporter; in the application launcher."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvoz "
"&kmail; Podatki...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> skozi okno za ogled sporočila "
"ali pa zaženete &i18n-pimdataexporter; kot samostojno aplikacijo z zagonom "
"&i18n-pimdataexporter; v zaganjalniku aplikacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To perform a backup, <action>select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Back Up Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice></action>, it "
"will prompt you to close all kdepim applications. <warning><para>Make sure "
"you close all windows, data loss is possible if you don't.</para></warning> "
"Once you have closed them, click <guibutton>Yes</guibutton> to continue, or "
"<guibutton>No</guibutton> to cancel."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvesti varnostno kopiranje, <action>izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Varnostno kopiraj "
"podatke...</guimenuitem></menuchoice></action>, pozvalo vas bo, da zaprete "
"vse kdepim aplikacije. <warning><para>Prepričajte se, da ste zaprli vsa "
"okna, sicer je možna izguba podatkov.</para></warning> Ko jih zaprete, "
"kliknite <guibutton>Da</guibutton> za nadaljevanje ali <guibutton>Ne</"
"guibutton> za preklic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will be prompted to create a backup name, enter the name into the "
"<guilabel>File</guilabel> textbox, &eg; <replaceable>mymailsettings</"
"replaceable>. The default filetype it saves as is <filename role=\"extension"
"\">.zip</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Pozvani boste, da ustvarite ime varnostne kopije, vnesite ime v besedilno "
"polje <guilabel>Datoteka</guilabel>, npr. <replaceable>mymailsettings</"
"replaceable>. Privzeta vrsta datoteke, kot jo shrani, je <filename role="
"\"extension\">.zip</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next screen will allow you to select what you wish to backup, by default "
"everything is selected."
msgstr ""
"Na naslednjem zaslonu boste lahko izbrali, kaj želite varnostno kopirati, "
"privzeto je izbrano vse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; Mails selection will only backup mails in your <quote>Local Folders</"
"quote>, it will backup &imap; settings and download messages upon restore. "
"If you have emails on a &imap; server you wish to be backed up, you should "
"use <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_folderarchive_agent\">Folder Archive Agent</"
"ulink> to archive those emails to a local folder."
msgstr ""
"Izbira e-pošte &kmail; bo varnostno kopirala samo e-pošto v vaših "
"<quote>Lokalnih mapah</quote>, varnostno bo kopirala &imap; nastavitve in "
"prenesla sporočila po obnovitvi. Če imate e-pošto na &imap; strežnika, za "
"katerega želite varnostno kopijo, uporabite <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_folderarchive_agent\">Sredstvo za arhiviranje map</ulink> za "
"arhiviranje teh e-poštnih sporočil v lokalno mapo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Selection Dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbirno pogovorno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Selection Dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbirno pogovorno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Selection Dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Izbirno pogovorno okno</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The final screen shows the log of the backup up process. You can close the "
"window once you have reviewed the log and verified your backup was "
"successful."
msgstr ""
"Končni zaslon prikazuje dnevnik postopka varnostnega kopiranja. Okno lahko "
"zaprete, ko pregledate dnevnik in preverite, ali je bila varnostna kopija "
"uspešna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To restore your backup, select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Restore Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> within &i18n-"
"pimdataexporter;."
msgstr ""
"Če želite obnoviti varnostno kopijo, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Obnovi podatke...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> znotraj "
"&i18n-pimdataexporter;ja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Archive "
"Information</guimenuitem></menuchoice> you can select a backup archive and "
"view its content."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži "
"informacije o arhivu</guimenuitem></menuchoice> lahko izberete varnostno "
"kopijo arhiva in si ogledate njegovo vsebino."

